    <para><guimenu>Description:</guimenu> Determines the internet protocol version of the given driver (<parameter>network()</parameter> or <parameter>syslog()</parameter>). The possible values are <parameter>4</parameter> and <parameter>6</parameter>, corresponding to IPv4 and IPv6. The default value is <parameter>4</parameter>.</para>
